divs: sighting detailsi took this picture on june 23 2009 at 7:47pm on my cell phone. i was on vacation at dale hollow lake in tn\ky. i took a picture of the sunset from the top of the houseboat that we were on. i didn't look at the picture until the next day. this is what i discovered. a flying saucer in front of the sun. from the shows i've seen, ufos fly so fast through vortexes that the human eye can rarely see them, however pictures can capture them. i did not see the flying saucer with my bare eyes, or maybe i did but my eyes didn't register it. i would like to know your opinions about this and if there are any other sightings in this area. it is also important to note that there is a military presence in the area.
